(47, 1, '2024-02-28 21:36:27', '2024-02-28 21:36:27', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Welcome</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to Sally Sweets, where the magic of sweets meets the charm of our versatile events room. This dedicated space serves as the canvas for an array of delightful events, from nostalgic adult nights to vibrant children\'s parties. Whether you\'re planning a corporate function, a birthday celebration, or a baby shower, our side room offers the perfect backdrop for your sweet gatherings.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Get in touch today to book your event!</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our events</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Private bookings are available, allowing you to tailor the space to your specific needs and preferences. Immerse yourself in the world of confectionery delights as you create memories in an environment designed for sweetness and celebration.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Adults only events</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At Sally Sweets, we believe adults deserve their sweet moments too. Join us for Retro Night, a journey back in time with classic sweets and tunes. For the sophisticated palate, indulge in our Chocolate Extravaganza or experience the perfect pairing of wine and sweets.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Childrens Parties</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Make your child\'s special day unforgettable with Candyland Adventure, filled with exciting games and sweet treats. Engage their creativity with our DIY Cupcake Decoration event, or let them meet their favourite characters in our Character-themed Party. Each event is curated for joy and excitement, ensuring a sweet celebration for the little ones.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Private Functions</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sally Sweets transforms corporate events into delightful experiences with tailored sweet packages. Our side room is also the ideal venue for birthday celebrations, offering customizable options suitable for all ages. Welcoming a new member of the family? Celebrate the upcoming arrival with sweet treats and a warm atmosphere at our baby showers. Whatever the occasion, Sally Sweets is here to make your private functions as sweet as can be.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Call us not to find out more</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Event sweet packages</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Choose from a variety of sweet packages to elevate your event experience. The Sweet Sampler is perfect for a small gathering, offering a mix of popular candies. Dive into a world of chocolate with the Chocoholic\'s Delight, an exclusive package for chocolate enthusiasts. For a self-serve delight, the Candy Buffet provides a colourful array of sweets for guests to enjoy at their leisure. Our event packages are designed to cater to different preferences and themes, ensuring a sweet touch to every occasion.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><ul class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-col items-center md:items-start\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-color: currentcolor; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-vi