(172, 1, '2024-03-02 12:52:52', '2024-03-02 12:52:52', 'Gardners have long been one of the leading American chocolate manufacturers for their amazingly delicious and unique chocolate bars! Introducing the hugely popular S\'mores bar! It features a graham cracker biscuit base and a fluffy marshmallow core, all covered in smooth, thick milk chocolate! Think Walnut Whip minus the Walnut and with the addition of a graham cracker base! Yummy bars, just like those childhood campfire treats. *For an extra gooey, delicious experience, simply remove the wrapper and microwave for 3 to 5 seconds. Imported from the USA', 'Gardener\'s S\'mores Bar 42g', 'Introducing the hugely popular S\'mores bar! It features a graham cracker biscuit base and a fluffy marshmallow core', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'gardeners-smores-bar-42g', '', '', '2024-03-05 19:52:34', '2024-03-05 19:52:34', '', 0, 'http://sallysweets-wp.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=172', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(173, 1, '2024-03-02 13:05:16', '2024-03-02 13:05:16', '<p class=\"text-sm\">Awesome Reds flavours include a variety of delicious red fruit flavours that will send your taste buds into overdrive. Packed in a bag, and individually wrapped, makes it easy for everyone to pick their favourite red flavour. Jolly Rancher Awesome Reds Hard Candy are fruit-flavoured candies in four red varieties; Cherry, Watermelon, Fruit Punch and Strawberry. 186g. Imported from the USA.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font-bold pt-2\"><strong>Ingredients:</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"text-sm\">Corn Syrup, Sugar, Contains 2% or less of: Malic Acid, Natural and Artificial Flavor, Artificial Colour (Red 40, Blue 1, Yellow 6), Mineral Oil, Soy Lecithin.</p>', 'Jolly Rancher Awesome Reds Hard Candy', 'Awesome Reds flavours include a variety of delicious red fruit flavours that will send your taste buds into overdrive.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'jolly-rancher-awesome-reds-hard-candy', '', '', '2024-03-05 19:52:54', '2024-03-05 19:52:54', '', 0, 'http://sallysweets-wp.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=173', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(174, 1, '2024-03-02 13:05:10', '2024-03-02 13:05:10', 'The Hershey\'s strawberries N cream bars are ice cream inspired chocolate bars with a deliciously creamy strawberries and cream flavour. These yummy bars deliver a mess-free ice cream experience and is available in two more delightful flavours.', 'Hershey\'s Strawberries N Creme Bar', 'The Hershey\'s strawberries N cream bars are ice cream inspired chocolate bars', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'hersheys-strawberries-n-creme-bar', '', '', '2024-03-05 19:52:49', '2024-03-05 19:52:49', '', 0, 'http://sallysweets-wp.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=174', 0, 'product', '', 0),
