(184, 1, '2024-03-02 13:17:49', '2024-03-02 13:17:49', '<p class=\"text-sm\">Sour Patch Kids, first they\'re sour, then they\'re sweet! For those who enjoy the sour more than the sweet, The Sour Patch Kids Extreme Sour Share Bag is packed with fun, soft and chewy sweets with five extremely sour fruity flavours. Guaranteed mouth-watering fun! Sealed in a theatre box to help keep the candy flavourful and soft.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font-bold pt-2\"><strong>Ingredients:</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"text-sm\">Sugar, Invert Sugar Syrup, Glucose Syrup, Modified Maize Starch, Acids (Lactic Acid, Tartaric Acid, Citric Acid), Flavouring, Colours (E102, E110, E129, E133). Warning: E102, E110 and E129 may have an adverse effect on activity and attention in children.</p>', 'Sour Patch Kids Extreme Sour Theatre Box 99g', 'Sour Patch Kids, first they\'re sour, then they\'re sweet!', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'sour-patch-kids-extreme-sour-theatre-box-99g', '', '', '2024-03-05 19:48:44', '2024-03-05 19:48:44', '', 0, 'http://sallysweets-wp.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=184', 0, 'product', '', 0),
