(186, 1, '2024-03-02 13:23:30', '2024-03-02 13:23:30', 'Warheads Ooze Chews are oozing with sour flavour. With six mouth-puckering flavours to choose from these chewy treats are filled with a sour goo candy, the perfect combination of sweet and sour. Flavours include mango, strawberry, green apple, black cherry, watermelon and blue raspberry. Since 1985, WARHEADS® has set the standard for sour candy. Today WARHEADS is still the candy of choice for the super sour seekers.', 'Warheads Sour Ooze Chewz Theatre Box', 'Warheads Ooze Chews are oozing with sour flavour.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'warheads-sour-ooze-chewz-theatre-box', '', '', '2024-03-05 19:49:15', '2024-03-05 19:49:15', '', 0, 'http://sallysweets-wp.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=186', 0, 'product', '', 0),
