(188, 1, '2024-03-02 13:23:19', '2024-03-02 13:23:19', '<p class=\"text-sm\">Warheads have taken their sour expertise with candy and applied it to jelly beans to create a chewy, fruity, sour sensation for your taste buds! Warheads Sour Jelly Beans come in 6 delicious sour sugar coated flavours: Orange, Watermelon, Lemon, Blue Raspberry, Cherry, Green Apple.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font-bold pt-2\"><strong>Ingredients:</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"text-sm\">Sugar, glucose syrup, modified corn starch, fumaric acid, flavourings, citric acid, colours (E129, E110, E102, E133). Warning: E102, E110 and E129 may have an adverse effect on activity and attention in children. Contains genetically modified ingredients. Warning: Sour products may cause irritation to the mouth Not recommended for children under 3 years of age.</p>', 'War heads sour jelly beans', 'Warheads have taken their sour expertise with candy and applied it to jelly beans to create a chewy, fruity, sour sensation for your taste buds!', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'war-heads-sour-jelly-beans', '', '', '2024-03-05 19:49:05', '2024-03-05 19:49:05', '', 0, 'http://sallysweets-wp.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=188', 0, 'product', '', 0),
