(190, 1, '2024-03-02 14:10:58', '2024-03-02 14:10:58', '<p class=\"text-sm\">Tasty white chocolate buttons, sprinkled with a multicoloured, light candy coating - what\'s not to love? The Kingsway Giant Snowies are a pick n mix favourite that kids both big and small adore! Both eye-catching and moreish.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font-bold pt-2\"><strong>Ingredients:</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"text-sm\">Sugar, vegetable fat (palm), whey powder (from milk), wheat flour (with added calcium, iron, niacin, thiamin)*, wheat starch, emulsifier: soya lecithin; glucose syrup, natural flavourings, natural colours: carotenes, betanin, anthocyanins; glazing agent: beeswax.</p>', 'Giant Snowies', 'Tasty white chocolate buttons, sprinkled with a multicoloured, light candy coating.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'giant-snowies', '', '', '2024-03-05 20:03:52', '2024-03-05 20:03:52', '', 0, 'http://sallysweets-wp.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=190', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(191, 1, '2024-03-02 14:10:53', '2024-03-02 14:10:53', '<p class=\"text-sm\">Blue and white, fruit-flavoured mini jellies in the shape of dolphins, are a new edition to the Vidal range of sweets - These are a jelly soft texture small Dolphin shape sweet which comes in two assorted random mixed colours of Blue and off white colours and is a mild fruity flavour.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font-bold pt-2\"><strong>Ingredients:</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"text-sm\">Glucose Syrup, Sugar, Gelatine, Humectant (Sorbitol), Corn Starch, Acid (Citric Acid), Flavourings, Vegetable Oils (Coconut, Palm Kernel), Glazing Agents (Beeswax, Carnauba Wax), Colours (E133, E171).</p>', 'Baby Dolphins - Blue and White', 'Blue and white, fruit-flavoured mini jellies in the shape of dolphins.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'baby-dolphins-blue-and-white', '', '', '2024-03-05 20:03:48', '2024-03-05 20:03:48', '', 0, 'http://sallysweets-wp.local/?post_type=product&#038;p=191', 0, 'product', '', 0),
